Package: ETVapp
Type: Package
Title: ETV/ICP-MS and -OES data processing functions and Shiny-App
Version: 0.4.3
Date: 2026-06-04
Authors@R: c(
    person("Jan", "Lisec", , "jan.lisec@bam.de", role = c("cre", "aut"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0003-1220-2286")),
    person("Vera", "Scharek", email = "vera.scharek@bam.de", role = c("aut", "ctb"))
  )
Description: Processing functions including a Shiny-App to evaluate data from (online) 
    Isotope dilution mass spectrometry experiments and other ETV/ICP-MS and -OES 
    based measurements. The package provides a generalized import function for
    typical data formats, different universal signal processing functions 
    (smoothing, peak picking etc.) and workflow specific output functions for
    tabulated results. A Shiny-App allows low level access to potential workflows
    while several vignettes show examples for the more versatile approach of
    combining package functions in reproducible processing scipts.
